text: Everyone talks about antivaxxers and vaccine proponents, but no one ever mentions vaccine centrism: Switch to injecting all vaccines INTRADERMALLY instead of intramuscularly. It would prevent 99% of weird systematic inflammatory reactions and still works enough for herd immunity.

Intradermal vaccination should be the default and intramuscular vaccination should only be used in communities with high risk factors or where the disease is still an active issue. The immune reaction is different between the two with less antibodies produced but no side effects.
